<entry stylesheet="mo:info/styles/guide.css">
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">The $itemName</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">The $itemName is used to refine [item name=matter_dust] into [item name=matter_dust_refined]. That allows the recycling of any [item name=matter_dust] byproduct from replication or decomposing.</text>
        <image width="64" height="64" src="guide/matter_recycler_small.png" style="float:left;margin-right:4px"></image>
        <image width="159" height="64" src="guide/matter_recycler_wide.png"></image>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">How to use</title>
        <creates from="[item name=matter_dust]" to="[item name=matter_dust_refined]"></creates>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">By putting the [item name=matter_dust] in the input slot and providing power to the $itemName. You can recycle some [item name=matter_dust_refined]. You can then use it in a [item name=decomposer] to breakdown into [guide name=matter_plasma].</text>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <recipe style="text-align:center"></recipe>
    </page>
</entry>